text.tspan: Place one of your pieces in an empty square
Place the PYLON in any square
on top of the PYLON in an ADJACENT square
to form a combined PYLON in that square
ADJACENT: two squares sharing a side
PYLON: one or more pieces, stacked so that no piece is above a smaller piece
DON'T rearrange pieces in a PYLON
1 POINT for each piece in any PYLON
whose top piece is of their colour
